WEBVTT

00:00:00.532 --> 00:00:04.644
Let's talk dirty.

00:00:04.644 --> 00:00:07.380
A few years ago, oddly enough,

00:00:07.380 --> 00:00:10.114
I needed the bathroom,

00:00:10.114 --> 00:00:13.464
and I found one, a public bathroom,

00:00:13.464 --> 00:00:15.828
and I went into the stall,

00:00:15.828 --> 00:00:19.125
and I prepared to do what I'd done most of my life:

00:00:19.125 --> 00:00:23.667
use the toilet, flush the toilet, forget about the toilet.

00:00:23.667 --> 00:00:25.748
And for some reason that day, instead,

00:00:25.748 --> 00:00:27.932
I asked myself a question,

00:00:27.932 --> 00:00:31.808
and it was, where does this stuff go?